hcc_text: Hutch River Parkway East is in the middle third in the Bronx for pedestrian deaths and serious injuries per mile.
info: At Hutch River Parkway East at Pelham Parkway South and Continental Avenue, there was 1 severe injury in crashes between 2008 and 2012.
